text: Northern Calloway (January 22, 1948) was an American actor, voice artist, and comedian. He is best known for playing David on Sesame Street from 1971 through 1989. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:Comedians from New York City Category:1948 births Category:1990 deaths Category:Actors from New York City
